<article>
<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p>TechTerms takes your privacy seriously.  We do not sell or redistribute any personal information.  The TechTerms website and mobile apps do not collect or store information about individual users.</p>
<h3>Cookies</h3>
<p>Quizzes and advertisements served on TechTerms.com may place and read <a href="/definition/cookie">cookies</a> within your web browser or use Web beacons to collect information.  You may choose to limit the cookies you accept by modifying your browser's security preferences.  Google may use DART cookies, which allow targeted ads to be served to your Web browser. If you wish to opt out of DART cookie use, please visit Google's <a href="http://www.google.com/privacy/ads/" target="_blank">Advertising and Privacy page</a>.</p>
<h3>Questions</h3>
<p>If you have questions regarding this privacy policy, you may <a href="/contact">contact TechTerms</a>.</p>
